    public interface TableGroupInfo
    Access to "source" information about a TableGroup to be built - a set of parameters indicating information to encode into the TableGroup. This information varies depending on the particular source (HQL, loading, etc). Intended use is as a "parameter object" for TableGroupProducer methods.
